des: The 2022 California Proposition Guide is an interactive voter guide created by KQED to help you better understand California’s 7 state propositions. Hear from KQED reporters on the propositions that matter most to you. Listen to an overview of any state proposition by asking for it by number or even brief description. You can also learn more by asking, “What does a yes or no vote mean? Who supports or opposes this proposition?” You can also hear about ways to vote in the upcoming election.
